NODE
 - is online/offline
 - is published
 - is descended (vidim jeho synov)
 - has color
 - is star
 - export: No, With content, Without content
 - sortable/tree
 - versioned
 - exportable
 - can be associated with n other nodes
 - ma copy, delete, move, duplicate
 - ma unikatny typ v ramci site id a svojho typu

